                    <strong>Portainer shows "API version too old" error</strong>
                    <p>This is a known issue with Docker 29.x. Fix it with:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Run <code>sudo systemctl edit docker.service</code></li>
                        <li>Add: <code>[Service]</code> and <code>Environment=DOCKER_MIN_API_VERSION=1.24</code></li>
                        <li>Save, then run <code>sudo systemctl restart docker</code></li>
                        <li>Finally: <code>docker compose restart portainer</code></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="troubleshooting-item">
